Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FIRST CAKE WE MAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem to be in good health...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I equip the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Bring lots of milk!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do I go to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't count on Heinz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The car may be suitable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you looking for apricot jam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate it at London, at Dennis' house,\Nit was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is apricot jam here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not this brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me who is the manufacturer,\Nthen I can order it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall who the manufacturer is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I look at the brand myself\NI will remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Also...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If we order it from abroad,\Nit will take several weeks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked it\Nif my grandfather had tried it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to check for in the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? I'll be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Leighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you want?\NI'll go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Will you go alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm big enough enough to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to travel in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to travel on the seat!\NThe important thing is to go to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can go anywhere in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, it's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a car parked in front of our store!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a car from the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome Mr. Cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guess what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Today my order is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show me all kinds\Nof apricot jam you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Colin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you because of this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, this is confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to ask Miss for its exact shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you allow me to call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will turn you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A brown dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful and lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As I mention its name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it named Lassie then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the name of the owner of that dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood, I finally know his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie and John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I... am going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want to show me about John's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go on that path you\Nwill find two straight roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the left road,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find adjacent houses\Nbelonging to the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those continuous descent that resemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the house number?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... house number... as I recall... is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The houses are really similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Does John live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know his name or address,\Nyet you go to him! So strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? And what do you\Nwant from John? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I did something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- This place?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if John is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,John is in the backyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What a nice Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah... um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What a strange boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend came!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A long hair blonde miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I asked her to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She is waiting for you on the couch\Nin the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she really knew my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous, you will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah ah ah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah ah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at yourself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'll change my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey John!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up, Lassie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We met again, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Lassie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you got to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie will host you until John\Ncomes, please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This host is my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? Does that girl know me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is still beating faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected that girl is definitely Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the kid who was in the food store!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a girl in blue clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She is between 11 and 12 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did not this person here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does this uncle chase me?\NI haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this child running away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? I can't remove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll enter, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should wash it with warm water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought eggs and cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't seem to know you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,About this... she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such thing doesn't matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right! Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected from John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John still acts like a child!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,True true, when we went to the canal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, then she is your friend, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's wrong, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He finally came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello John!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin told me about your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad smell! Bad smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like paint, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to prepare cakes\Nwhen you are on holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Sandy to come,\Nand bring eggs and cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea! Because we have guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,John's clothes are dirty because of the paint\Nand they must be washed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wash it, so make the cakes, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be made by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy told me she would make the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Priscilla? You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't made cakes before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She does what she always wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always with your owner, right?\NYou are lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to wash clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will look forward to the cake you will make!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you make it while you are three?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And John will light up the fireplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Priscilla, an egg!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priscilla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Separate the glair from the yolk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mix water and milk!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have ignited the fireplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't move your hand like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, I'll do this again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes teacher, do this for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it until it appears in the form of horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Horns? Like cow horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, here are the horns, Priscilla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we will wait until it is baked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed making cakes with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What food should I feed this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pour water and sugar on cotton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Water and sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is unfortunate that you put it\Nin such a narrow place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to put it, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First to prepare arable soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...then it is better to plant a tree in it, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't run anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How does it looks?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good appetite!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Welcome back!\N- Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to come back and\Nfind such a fine smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiffon cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your mother made it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But these two girls made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry for the intrusion!\N- Sorry for the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, to complete our conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this smell is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected the Duke brought\Nhis granddaughter with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He will visit us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That place is not for the children to see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have come out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because I grew unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin also came!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,John, I brought a strange man with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault because\Nyou didn't listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leighton! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you stop kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You hid in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you were abducted\Nor something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:20:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst because I did what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made Leighton pass a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not bad... Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to your looks I have\Nidentified many people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy, thank you for telling me\Nhow to make cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of that thing you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The little jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Colin, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's it.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for what happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't eat any piece of cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I heard the name of Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla... Priscilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The granddaughter of the\Nmine owner is called Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,True, that uncle came from that palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad, I seem to have said\Nsomething very terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a job you did, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You just heard the talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Priscilla's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- You should taste a piece of this cake!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Priscilla will return tonight to Scotland.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though she has good friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's all go to the Rocky Castle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to see places\Nyou haven't seen before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NPRISCILLA, LAST SELFISHNESS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
